{"name":"5005410142019d3ed2e3","layouts":[{"id":0,"position":{"x":644.373576309795,"y":46.651480637813215,"z":1000,"width":624.9354593773729,"height":665.7555049354594}}],"singleVisual":{"visualType":"textbox","drillFilterOtherVisuals":true,"objects":{"general":[{"properties":{"paragraphs":[{"textRuns":[{"value":"The Six Square Segmentation Grid is a tool that groups all of an institutions constituents into six segments based their Annual Giving Probability to Donate Index (AG PDI) and Annual Giving Expected Value Index (AG EVI) scores. The Green segment represents those most likely to donate to annual giving and also most likely to donate at high values; the Orange segment represents those with the lowest expected value and lowest average probability to donate."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":""}]},{"textRuns":[{"value":"All Revenue and Production totals include both \"Forward Blue\" Campaign gifts as well as non-Campaign gifts (although there are not many non-Campaign transactions currently, there will be many once we pass the end of the Forward Blue Campaign)."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":""}]},{"textRuns":[{"value":"On"},{"value":" the \"Production Focus\" and \"Revenue Focus\" tabs, the \"Total Production/Revenue by Category\" represents the total by Campaign \"Bucket\" (\"Scholarships\", \"Mission, Academics & Programs\", and \"Student Experience\").","textStyle":{"fontSize":"12px"}}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"On the same tabs, the \"Parent Program Category\" is similar to \"Finance Category\" displayed on other reports, but also breaks out gift to the \"Parent Fund\", \"Men's BB Auxiliary Income\" and \"Other Athletics Gifts\". Because of this additional breakout, the \"regular\" Finance Categories will not reconcile to Finance Category totals shown on other reports.","textStyle":{"fontSize":"12px"}}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"On the same tabs, if you add together \"Annual Scholarships\" and \"Endowed Scholarships\", the total will not reconcile to the respective totals on the Scholarship tab. This is because of the Parent Program category of \"Other Athletics Gifts\", which includes some Athletics scholarships."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":""}]},{"textRuns":[{"value":"The \"Students\" tab displays all Current Students linked to one or more Parents in Advance for the current FY. This page is not connected to the FY Slicer and so will only display the current year's Current Students and will not display stats for students who are not linked to Parents."}],"listType":"bullet"}]}}]},"vcObjects":{"border":[{"properties":{"show":{"expr":{"Literal":{"Value":"true"}}}}}]}}}

{"name":"a20a10427a58ab08907d","layouts":[{"id":0,"position":{"x":10.690964312832195,"y":46.651480637813215,"z":0,"width":624.9354593773729,"height":665.7555049354594}}],"singleVisual":{"visualType":"textbox","drillFilterOtherVisuals":true,"objects":{"general":[{"properties":{"paragraphs":[{"textRuns":[{"value":"To be a \"Current Parent\" an entity must have a relationship in Advance as a \"Parent\" linked to a \"Child\" who is coded as a \"Current Student\". Thus, a Current Parent will be counted even if they do not have a \"Current Parent\" record type."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"For a Current Parent to count in any given Fiscal Year, the Current Student's Start date must be before the last day of the FY and their Stop Date must be after the first day of the FY (or have no Stop Date\")."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"\"PLC Members\" are counted in a given FY if they were active for even one day of that FY, based on their PLC Committee Start and Stop Dates."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"\"Alumni Parent\" counts are based on the current degree status of each Parent in the household; Non-Degreed Alumni are not counted (i.e. the Parent must have at least one earned degree row in Advance).","textStyle":{"fontSize":"13.3333px"}}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"\"Faculty/Staff Parents\" are counted in a given FY if they were active for even one day of that FY, based on their Employment row Start and Stop Dates. It is possible for entities to have more than one active employment row for Creighton, so counts could be slightly exaggerated (this is rare)."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"\"Assigned Parents\" are counted in a given FY if they were actively assigned to a Primary Manager for even one day of that FY, based on their Primary Manager Assignment row Start and Stop Dates. It is not uncommon for Parents to start a year assigned to one PM and then get reassigned to another PM. Therefore, a Current Parent household could be counted under each PM for which they were actively assigned in any given FY. Even so, counts of Assigned Current Parents are distinct (they are not counted twice in a FY even if they were assigned to two different PMs).","textStyle":{"fontSize":"13.3333px"}}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":""}]},{"textRuns":[{"value":"\"MG EVI\" is a Blackbaud score that provides a rank order of all prospects; scores range from 1 to 99 (with 99 being the highest possible rank) based on their expected value to Creighton next year."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"The Creighton \"Engagement Score\" is a proprietary measure of an entity's Creighton-related activity; scores range from 0 to 100, with 100 being the highest score reflecting the most-engaged entities."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":""}]},{"textRuns":[{"value":"\"Production FYTD\" and \"Revenue FYTD\", when set to the current FY represent the total Production/Revenue to date for the current FY. When the Fiscal Year slicer is set to a previous FY, the numbers represent the FYE totals for the selected FY."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"\"Household Donors\" and \"Individual Donors\" represent the counts of donors with soft credit > $0 for the selected FY. A donor is not counted if they were the \"Honored\" or \"Memorialized\" donor on a given transaction."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"The \"Count of Receipts\" represents a distinct count of receipts (Revenue) or transactions (Production) for the selected FY. (\"Production\" = pledges + outright gifts; \"Revenue\" = pledge payments + outright gifts.)"}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"The \"Average per HH\" represents the total Revenue/Production divided by the Count of Household Donors."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"\"Participation\" for both \"HH\" and \"Indiv\" is calculated by dividing the total number of \"HH/Individual\" donors by the total number of Households or Individuals."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"The \"Avg Transaction\" is calculated by dividing the total Production/Revenue by the Count of Receipts/ Transactions."}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":"The colorful six-square visual represents the Blackbaud Six-Segment Scores for Current Parents. "}],"listType":"bullet"},{"textRuns":[{"value":""}]}]}}]},"vcObjects":{"border":[{"properties":{"show":{"expr":{"Literal":{"Value":"true"}}}}}]}}}
